						StaticText 'Three buttons: that’s all it takes to get the Switch game camera fully operational. This dummy-proof trail camera from Wildgame Innovations is the easiest setup we’ve ever come up with. Choose a capture mode, delay setting and time zone – and you’re done. The Switch captures crisp 12 megapixel images and 720p HD videos, and updates the date and time automatically (even during Daylight Savings). Spend your time hunting, not setting up cameras, with the Switch Cam.
